      <title>韩国致命爆炸再次引发对电池安全的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/deadly-battery-explosion-in-korea-reignites-fears-over-safety</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国是全球主要的锂离子电池供应国，其生产的电池广泛应用于电动汽车、储能系统等多个领域，一场致命的工厂火灾再次引发了人们对电池安全的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/deadly-battery-explosion-in-korea-reignites-fears-over-safety</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 05:29:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度称太阳能电池产量增长将抑制中国进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/india-says-rising-solar-cell-output-will-curb-imports-from-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最高可再生能源官员表示，预计未来几个月国内太阳能电池生产能力将大幅提升，这将有助于减少其对从中国进口太阳能电池板制造材料的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/india-says-rising-solar-cell-output-will-curb-imports-from-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 05:17:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
